      <li class="ctsh clearfix" data-cid="31976097">
        <div class="ilst">
          <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/48667066/"><img src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u48667066-4.jpg" alt="无端耳朵" class="" /></a>
        </div>
        <div class="con">
          <div class="nlst">
            <h3>
              <div class="note-toggle rr">
                <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/31976097/" class="note-unfolder">展开</a>
                <a href="javascript:void(0);" class="note-folder">收起</a>
              </div>
              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/31976097/" class="">第55页</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/48667066/" class=" " title="无端耳朵">无端耳朵</a>
              
            </p>
            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="31976097">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">这很奇怪，我在等一个信号，一个预示着发生了什么的信号。但是每次我睁开眼睛，一切还是老样子。</span>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2014-06-19 22:31</span>
                  
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
                <blockquote><q>这很奇怪，我在等一个信号，一个预示着发生了什么的信号。但是每次我睁开眼睛，一切还是老样子。</q></blockquote>
                  <div class="col-rec-con clearfix">
                    







<div class="rec-sec">

    <span class="rec">

<a href="https://www.douban.com/accounts/register?reason=collect" class="j a_show_login lnk-sharing lnk-douban-sharing">推荐</a>
</span>
</div>

                  </div>
                <div class="pl col-time">
                  <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/31976097/#comments">回应</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;
                  2014-06-19 22:31
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
